<div class="content" name="DFSM_ROOT_LIST_ENTRY" uuid="6ea1250f-867e-4d69-8e63-a8446329ffd0"><p>The DFSM_ROOT_LIST_ENTRY structure relates to the <a href="eff0144e-26d7-485c-aeed-caa737bcd7d2" data-linktype="relative-path">NetrDfsAdd2</a>, <a href="eddab804-70e9-4b78-9763-d4cb6f052496" data-linktype="relative-path">NetrDfsAddFtRoot</a>, and <a href="d2d8d56c-7ff6-4674-8193-313ddf1f1c3b" data-linktype="relative-path">NetrDfsSetInfo2</a> methods
when used to add a <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_0611e93d-f0e7-42ee-a591-d77ebcbb6619" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS link</a>
or a <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_ac90b498-3ba4-48d6-bcd6-5495f1654671" data-linktype="relative-path">DFS root target</a>, or
to modify the configuration of a <a href="a9bc4403-a862-48b9-b99b-1b44a887d177#gt_133ab305-ad75-4b38-8ec9-40bc0dc3b594" data-linktype="relative-path">domain-based DFS namespace</a>.
The structure contains information about a DFS root target. </p><p>The DFSM_ROOT_LIST_ENTRY structure has the following format.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef struct _DFSM_ROOT_LIST_ENTRY {
   [string, unique] WCHAR* ServerShare;
 } DFSM_ROOT_LIST_ENTRY;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>ServerShare:</b>  Specifies a DFS root
target.</p></div>